WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.000
Not all applicants will have the opportunity to participate in an admissions 

00:02.000 --> 00:04.000
interview. Select applicants will be invited to meet with members of the 

00:04.000 --> 00:06.000
admissions committee during one of the Candidate Weekends, which will take place 

00:06.000 --> 00:09.000
in Abu Dhabi. All eligible candidates will be contacted by NYU Abu 

00:09.000 --> 00:11.000
Dhabi to arrange for this visit. Whenever possible, we encourage all applicants 

00:11.000 --> 00:13.000
to visit the NYU Abu Dhabi campus or attend an information session 

00:13.000 --> 00:16.000
in their city or region. 

